{"tid":2227421,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Brewster 23.5M由利記轉投錫菲聯","createTime":"2020-10-02T18:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T09:59:15.000Z","uid":119729,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b66c92f2869e12092b7217546f57eba782f012","tid":2227421,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:39:02.000Z","msg":"The England youth international departs Anfield after five years, though the Reds will retain a buy-back option on the forward<br />\n<br />\nSheffield United have completed the signing of striker Rhian Brewster from Liverpool in a club-record &pound;23.5 million ($30m) deal.<br />\n<br />\nThe 20-year-old spent five seasons with the Reds, where he progressed through the club's academy to become a member of the senior squad.<br />\n<br />\nBrewster, though, made just four appearances for Liverpool and has now departed in a bid to earn more minutes at the Premier League level. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.goal.com/en-us/amp/news/sheffield-united-confirm-235m-brewster-signing-from/p2tzxdqxy23t1u3po28y6qdac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.goal.com%2Fen-us%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fsheffield-united-confirm-235m-brewster-signing-from%2Fp2tzxdqxy23t1u3po28y6qdac&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmcjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=5a750d84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.goal.com/en-us/amp/news/sheffield-united-confirm-235m-brewster-signing-from/p2tzxdqxy23t1u3po28y6qdac</a><br />\n<br />\n利狗D轉會操作唔講得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一場英超都無踢過，賣到咁貴"},{"pid":"cbce1744e4ff98dd71f5a6d7a38adad8389bef76","tid":2227421,"uid":352074,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T20:16:59.000Z","msg":"佢都係好心幫利儲錢買包皮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f1661b210f883d74dd3814595766762e90e